Subject: [Bioc-devel] More than 1 citation in landing page
In-Reply-To: <35638_1414754006_54536ED6_35638_10083_1_CAP8VEO7yNnEdvZdds7diHoPZ=RqQCXAC6Lb-Z0cgzmy7H5u=mw@mail.gmail.com>
